stories.text:
I've been wanting to make these cards for many many years because they are something I would want to use myself, but couldn't find the time until COVID.

The synopsis is that so much of intelligence is just asking the right questions, and it's not something we have a lot of space for in the rush of the modern day world, so the cards help create that space so we can better contemplate our businesses.

Hope you enjoy
